v_products_description_1: Chef's Choice
Fresh-made French onion soup topped with toasted French bread and melted Swiss cheese
Inspired by the hearty soups of the northwoods lumber camps, this soup blends juicy chicken chunks into Grandma's award-winning, rich and creamy, wild rice soup
Not Julius. But it does rule! Crisp romaine lettuce topped with herb croutons and Parmesan cheese. Rosa's classic Caesar dressing on the side.

This flavorful salad features breast of chicken coated with sesame seed breading and is served warm over a bed of mixed greens, with toasted sesame seeds and fried wontons. Ginger and rice wine vinaigrette on the side.
A plump boneless breast of chicken char grilled and served warm over mixed greens and Roma tomatoes and blue cheese crumbles. House-made raspberry vinaigrette on the side.

A generous portion of tender grilled chicken breast, combined with Minnesota long-grain wild rice, plumped craisins, golden raisins, shredded carrot, and diced red and green peppers mixed with Grandma's creamy sweet dressing. Served with fresh seasonal fruit and cranberry/wild rice toast points

Grandma's version of the classic Cobb salad features a plump, juicy chicken breast char grilled and placed atop a bed of chopped romaine lettuce topped with smoky bacon, blue cheese crumbles, guacamole, sliced boiled egg, tomatoes, red onion, carrots, and cucumbers. Served with your choice of dressing
Not Julius. But it does rule! Crisp romaine lettuce topped with herb croutons and Parmesan cheese. Rosa's classic Caesar dressing on the side.
The one that made Rosa the "Burger Queen" of Duluth. Burger, grilled onion, bun, fries. Simple, yet elegant
Featuring thick-cut smokehouse bacon and cheddar cheese
Topped with sauteed marinated mushrooms and Swiss cheese
Burger aficionados have been flocking to Grandma's for years to delve into this legend. Two all-beef patties topped with grilled onions, sauteed mushrooms, mozzarella, cheddar, and American cheeses
Served with fresh leaf lettuce and fresh tomato slices on a bun slathered with mayo
The one that made Rosa the "Burger Queen" of Duluth. Burger, melted American cheese, grilled onion, bun, fries. Simple, yet elegant

Look, Ma no meat! This popular burger features Minnesota wild rice hand-pattied burgers with sharp cheddar cheese and a blend of secret ingredients. Topped with melted cheddar cheese and served on our wheat pub bun dressed with mayonnaise, lettuce, tomato, onions, carrots, and sprouts. Accompanied by a garden fresh salad with your choice of dressing

Juicy ground turkey spiked with Grandma's Good Stuff All Purpose seasoning, then grilled and topped with thick-cut smokehouse bacon, lettuce, and tomato on a butter-toasted wheat bun dressed with mayo.
Real Canadian walleye dipped in beer batter, breaded, and deep fried. Served on a buttered and toasted Tuscan baguette with our sweet house-made tartar sauce, lettuce, and tomato

This two-fisted sandwich has been in the family for years. Thinly sliced roast beef stacked high on a hearty Tuscan baguette and served warm with our rich au jus for dipping.They said the original couldn't be improved

This sandwich goes back to the beginning. It started out as a way to help folks stay warm during those cold winter nights. Today, it's enjoyed all year long! Lots of corned beef and pastrami smothered with melted Swiss, pepper cheese, and sliced sweet onions. Served on a buttered and toasted Tuscan baguette lightly spread with mustard

We actually found this recipe when we were going through some of Grandma's old valises. It was authored by a French immigrant from the East Coast. Grilled thick-sliced beef tenderloin and mushrooms smothered with mozzarella, cheddar, and Philadelphia cream cheese on a Tuscan baguette
A sesame breaded chicken breast, deep-fried, tossed with Buffalo Hot sauce, and topped with chunky blue cheese dressing served on an old-fashioned toasted bun. Almost as spicy as Rosa herself
A tender breast of chicken, grilled and topped with thick-cut smokehouse bacon and mozzarella cheese. Served on a fresh old-fashioned toasted bun
Char-grilled juicy chicken breast on a buttered and toasted ciabatta bun slathered with our succulent honey mustard sauce with lettuce, tomato, and alfalfa sprouts
Sliced smoked turkey breast, thick-sliced smokehouse bacon, lettuce, tomato, and mayonnaise served buttered and toasted cranberry-wild rice bread
Thinly cut corned beef brisket, Swiss cheese, and caraway seasoned sauerkraut, piled on thick-cut rye bread, grilled and served with a side of Thousand Island dressing
A show-stopping triple-decker Monte Cristo featuring thinly sliced ham, smoked turkey, Swiss and American cheese, layered on Texas toast with mayo, breaded and deep-fried. Served with fresh fruit
This two-fisted sandwich has been in the family for years. Thinly sliced roast beef stacked high on a hearty Tuscan baguette and served side of spicy giardiniera.
Roasted brussel sprouts sautéed in our homemade sweet chili glaze with bacon crumbles and red onion.
A large platter of our crispy French fries tossed with our famous Grandma's Good Stuff All Purpose Seasoning and served with ranch Dippin' sauce.

It's no secret that many a gentleman lost his heart to Rosa. She would often be showered with expensive gold rings in an attempt to win her over. They are the inspiration for our award-winning rings today?We challenge all comers to top our award-winning rings. Sweet, colossal onions dipped in beer batter, coated in toasted bread crumbs and deep-fried to a golden brown. Served with a complimentary side of dipping sauce.

A half dozen plump juicy bone-in traditional chicken wings flavored with your choice of sauce or dry rub. Sauces: Chipotle Mustard, Buffalo Cayenne, or Honey BBQ. Dry rubs: Good Stuff BBQ© or Mango-Habanero. Accompanied by one of our famous onion rings and one complimentary side of Dippin’ Sauce.
A gentleman's favorite. Large, fresh mushroom caps stuffed with wild rice and Mornay sauce, then topped with a blend of cheddar and Monterey Jack cheese and baked until bubbly hot
Four Jumbo butterflied shrimp seasoned, lightly breaded, and fried to a golden brown. Served with one side of tartar or cocktail sauce
Juicy chicken breast tenders breaded and deep-fried to a golden crisp. Served with your choice of two Dippin’ Sauces and French fries.
Caprese style slices of mozzarella with a light crunchy tomato-basil breading deep-fried and served with a side Grandma's legendary marinara sauce for dipping
Penne pasta blended with fresh basil, shaved garlic, black pepper, red pepper flakes,  crushed Roma tomatoes, and imported Parmesan.
